{"tid":1347872,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好令運動由民主運動變恐怖主義","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:25:27.000Z","uid":190579,"like":74,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"571f12dcb5bf799f12ad05259046d824026c9afd","tid":1347872,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">黑吃黑，江湖事江湖了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地千祈絕對唔撚好插手插嘴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好令場運動失焦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由民主運動變恐怖主義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑社會保持中立對我地最好</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n敵人既敵人唔係朋友<br />\n好似葉瘤你都唔會當朋友啦屌<br />\n切勿神化黑社會<br />\n<br />\n今日發生咩事 完全唔關我地事 大家當睇唔到 亦都唔好浪費熱門討論 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Focus番琴晚上環開咗槍呀 屌警犬老母!<br />\n<br />\n幫我推爆此po</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"7fd7733a7b73f75fea63e897f18232d21b9ec336","tid":1347872,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad057c40a2ac38c5adef8436307dea2c78b35a1f","tid":1347872,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dc07e13af75b3b45a3f7427f0471065fb12325c","tid":1347872,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"而家係國家恐襲平民"},{"pid":"80f3e83d0c13518bcf81270febce677a1303e03c","tid":1347872,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"你都ON9，如果香港有哈馬斯呢D組織先係最好進程"},{"pid":"4cf2e194bb292b039024daed13d1f8755e22519b","tid":1347872,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d57db95c9b2741da5d8ba2da031f50e4582d6960","tid":1347872,"uid":282987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc67086